%I A396337 #5 May 27 2026 00:24:50
%S A396337 0,4,127,11336,2761827,1891984647,3720952049343
%N A396337 Number of directed self-avoiding paths in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A396337 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
%C A396337 Excludes 0 length paths; including them increases each term by 1.
%e A396337 a(2) = 4, all symmetric and count as 1 each both undirected and directed:
%e A396337   X--X   X--+   X--+     X--+
%e A396337             |      |        |
%e A396337             X   X--+   ..X  +..
%e A396337 Nonsymmetric paths count as 2 each when directed, e.g.:
%e A396337   X--+--+      X>>+>>+       X<<+<<+
%e A396337         |  ->        v  and        ^
%e A396337         X            X             X
%Y A396337 Cf. A395462 (undirected), A394066 (wrapping disallowed).
%K A396337 nonn,walk,hard,more
%O A396337 1,2
%A A396337 _Charles L. Hohn_, May 22 2026
